'''阿丝贾·琼斯'''（{{lang-en|Asjha Jones}}，{{bd|1980年|8月1日||}}）生于新泽西州皮斯卡特维，是一名美国退役女子篮球运动员。她在3岁时开始接触篮球<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.teamusa.org/Athletes/JO/Asjha-Jones|title=Asjha Jones|work=[[美国奥林匹克与残疾人奥林匹克委员会|Team USA]]|accessdate=2021-03-01|archiveurl=https://archive.is/0aFig|archivedate=2021-03-01}}</ref>，1998年至2002年期间就读于[[康涅狄格大学|康涅狄格大学]]，并代表该校的女子篮球队参加校际比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://uconnhuskies.com/sports/womens-basketball/roster/asjha-jones/5728|title=Asjha Jones|work=UConn Huskies|accessdate=2021-03-01|archiveurl=https://archive.is/bCaWN|archivedate=2021-03-01}}</ref>。2012年曾随国家队参加伦敦奥运，结果获得金牌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/jo/asjha-jones-1.html|title=Asjha Jones|work=Sport Reference|accessdate=2021-03-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417134705/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/jo/asjha-jones-1.html|archivedate=2020-04-17}}</ref>。2015年WNBA赛季后，她结束了运动生涯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theday.com/article/20191001/SPORT13/191009938|title=Washington assistant Asjha Jones formed a lasting friendship with Thibault in Connecticut|publisher=The Day|date=2019-10-01|accessdate=2021-03-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004074322/https://www.theday.com/article/20191001/SPORT13/191009938|archivedate=2019-10-04}}</ref>。

